00:11:12.123 --> 00:11:17.333
husband, her daughter, three sons and her baby grandson.

00:11:18.733 --> 00:11:24.453
It was all over the national news, a sign of the lawlessness of these housing schemes

00:11:24.553 --> 00:11:30.233
and the inability of the Glasgow police to do its job and enforce law and order.

00:11:31.233 --> 00:11:36.513
There was a huge investigation, but nobody was willing to speak to the police.

00:11:37.193 --> 00:11:37.723
Nothing.

00:11:38.253 --> 00:11:39.233
Not a word.

00:11:40.773 --> 00:11:43.613
