00:20:42.288 --> 00:20:47.078
It isn’t quite correct to say that, but several housing schemes have banned them.

00:20:48.278 --> 00:20:53.318
It’s more from a public health point of view, to curb Scottish obesity rates,

00:20:53.708 --> 00:20:58.368
but certainly for many Glasgow residents who were alive during this period,

00:20:58.778 --> 00:21:03.338
the noise of an ice cream van brings back memories they would prefer to forget.

